        <section data-uuid="7da874aba27349e2886d5cb585002159" class="segment-opener">
            <article data-uuid="ff1918f5a9d34a24a856198ddf55d570">
                <h4 data-uuid="e99d7e3f887647e881bfdf586f62a34c">Main Idea</h4>
                <p class="main-idea" data-uuid="0cf7362228b740ea9f65c502bcf30290">Many American settlers moved to Texas after Mexico achieved independence from Spain.</p>
                <h2 data-uuid="d79fa27dc1754eb0a61792de6e302597">American Settlers Move to Texas</h2>
                <div data-uuid="2368560ff01747ff85ed33f1808f193d" class="yellow-star-yellow-bar"></div>
            </article>
        </section>
        <section data-uuid="19fbe41f1a414c21ae73d125cad6c088" class="graphic-organizer-prompt ">
            <div data-uuid="f05bba6776da432c99c558d13afca422" class="go-prompt-bottom-bar">
                <p data-uuid="f6355dd65da94a038cecbf12f0d09868">As you read, use the graphic organizer to take notes about the causes and effects of the Texas Revolution.</p>
